{"id":412581398,"lang":"python3","time":"8Â months, 1Â week","timestamp":1603544958,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"2688 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/412581398/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"3Sum","memory":"17.3 MB","code":"class Solution:\n    def threeSum(self, nums: List[int]) -> List[List[int]]:\n        # O(n^2) time | O(n) space\n        nums.sort()\n        result = set()\n        n = len(nums)\n        for i in range(n):\n            seen = set()\n            target = 0 - nums[i]\n            for j in range(i + 1, n):\n                if (target - nums[j]) in seen:\n                    result.add((nums[i], target - nums[j], nums[j]))\n                seen.add(nums[j])\n        return list(result)","compare_result":"","title_slug":"3sum"}
